[
{"inTime":"00:00:04.203","outTime":"00:00:05.498","caption":"Hi, I'm Anastasia. \n","textStyles":{"text-align":"center"}},
{"inTime":"00:00:05.503","outTime":"00:00:09.418","caption":"I'm one of the developers\nwho worked on the Infusion\nInline Edit component.\n","textStyles":{"text-align":"center"}},
{"inTime":"00:00:09.864","outTime":"00:00:14.720","caption":"The Inline Edit component\nallows a user to perform\nquick edits to any text,\n","textStyles":{"text-align":"center"}},
{"inTime":"00:00:14.721","outTime":"00:00:17.055","caption":" without having to switch\nmodes or screens.\n","textStyles":{"text-align":"center"}},
{"inTime":"00:00:17.241","outTime":"00:00:19.305","caption":"All the work is done on the\nsame interface\n","textStyles":{"text-align":"center"}},
{"inTime":"00:00:19.438","outTime":"00:00:22.297","caption":"which helps the user\nmaintain context.\n","textStyles":{"text-align":"center"}},
{"inTime":"00:00:23.593","outTime":"00:00:25.282","caption":"As the implementor,\n","textStyles":{"text-align":"center"}},
{"inTime":"00:00:25.348","outTime":"00:00:28.600","caption":"you have complete control over\nthe appearance of the text:\n","textStyles":{"text-align":"center"}},
{"inTime":"00:00:28.831","outTime":"00:00:30.815","caption":"the styling can be changed,\n","textStyles":{"text-align":"center"}},
{"inTime":"00:00:31.706","outTime":"00:00:34.745","caption":"a tooltip can be added,\n","textStyles":{"text-align":"center"}},
{"inTime":"00:00:35.109","outTime":"00:00:39.572","caption":"the text of the tooltip\ncan be customized,\n","textStyles":{"text-align":"center"}},
{"inTime":"00:00:40.716","outTime":"00:00:42.920","caption":"even the style can be changed.\n","textStyles":{"text-align":"center"}},
{"inTime":"00:00:45.758","outTime":"00:00:48.375","caption":"Inline Edit comes in three flavours:\n","textStyles":{"text-align":"center"}},
{"inTime":"00:00:48.376","outTime":"00:00:49.553","caption":"Simple Text,\n","textStyles":{"text-align":"center"}},
{"inTime":"00:00:49.554","outTime":"00:00:53.398","caption":"which allows users to\nedit plain text directly,\n","textStyles":{"text-align":"center"}},
{"inTime":"00:00:54.658","outTime":"00:00:56.602","caption":"Rich Text,\n","textStyles":{"text-align":"center"}},
{"inTime":"00:00:56.604","outTime":"00:00:58.945","caption":"which allows you to plug in\na rich-text editor,\n","textStyles":{"text-align":"center"}},
{"inTime":"00:00:58.946","outTime":"00:01:03.058","caption":"like the FCKEditor, or TinyMCE,\n","textStyles":{"text-align":"center"}},
{"inTime":"00:01:05.219","outTime":"00:01:06.640","caption":"and Drop-down,\n","textStyles":{"text-align":"center"}},
{"inTime":"00:01:06.641","outTime":"00:01:09.667","caption":"which presents a drop-down\nlist of choices.\n","textStyles":{"text-align":"center"}},
{"inTime":"00:01:10.391","outTime":"00:01:13.365","caption":"Support for 'undo' functionality\nis provided,\n","textStyles":{"text-align":"center"}},
{"inTime":"00:01:13.368","outTime":"00:01:17.155","caption":"allowing users to revert back\nto a previously saved value.\n","textStyles":{"text-align":"center"}},
{"inTime":"00:01:17.308","outTime":"00:01:20.355","caption":"If desired, the undo control\ncan be customized\n","textStyles":{"text-align":"center"}},
{"inTime":"00:01:20.356","outTime":"00:01:23.095","caption":"to use an image\ninstead of the default text.\n","textStyles":{"text-align":"center"}},
{"inTime":"00:01:24.186","outTime":"00:01:26.125","caption":"Like all Infusion components,\n","textStyles":{"text-align":"center"}},
{"inTime":"00:01:26.129","outTime":"00:01:28.642","caption":"the Inline Edit fires various events\n","textStyles":{"text-align":"center"}},
{"inTime":"00:01:28.643","outTime":"00:01:31.412","caption":"that your application can\nlisten for and act upon.\n","textStyles":{"text-align":"center"}},
{"inTime":"00:01:31.688","outTime":"00:01:32.590","caption":"In this example,\n","textStyles":{"text-align":"center"}},
{"inTime":"00:01:32.591","outTime":"00:01:35.780","caption":"the application is listening for\nthe 'modelChanged' event\n","textStyles":{"text-align":"center"}},
{"inTime":"00:01:35.781","outTime":"00:01:38.265","caption":"and displaying a\n'save' confirmation.\n","textStyles":{"text-align":"center"}},
{"inTime":"00:01:39.706","outTime":"00:01:43.200","caption":"The Inline Edit component\nis accessible in\nmany different ways.\n","textStyles":{"text-align":"center"}},
{"inTime":"00:01:43.313","outTime":"00:01:45.373","caption":"As I'm showing in this example,\n","textStyles":{"text-align":"center"}},
{"inTime":"00:01:45.378","outTime":"00:01:48.475","caption":"all of its functionality,\nfrom discovery to editing,\n","textStyles":{"text-align":"center"}},
{"inTime":"00:01:48.479","outTime":"00:01:51.460","caption":"can be carried out entirely\nusing the keyboard.\n","textStyles":{"text-align":"center"}},
{"inTime":"00:01:52.312","outTime":"00:01:52.812","caption":"","textStyles":[]}
]
